<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Flutter on 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/categories/flutter/</link><description>Recent content in Flutter on 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2019 16:03:03 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/categories/flutter/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Flutter开发App常见问题解决方案</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2019/12/13/flutter%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91app%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2019 16:03:03 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2019/12/13/flutter%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91app%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Flutter开发真的会遇到各种各样的坑爹问题，Android运行起来了可能发现iOS出问题了。遇到过不少问题，因此写这个文章做个汇总，也免得以后遇到了再次翻车。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>flutter命令行出现startup lock</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2019/09/09/flutter%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0startup-lock/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2019 16:06:17 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2019/09/09/flutter%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0startup-lock/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;有时候执行flutter命令会出现&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Waiting for another flutter command to release the startup lock...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;这是因为前一次的命令没有正常结束。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;解决方案很简单：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;去目录&lt;code&gt;flutter/bin/cache/lockfile&lt;/code&gt; 删除&lt;code&gt;lockfile&lt;/code&gt;文件，然后重新执行命令即可。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>